Gets the start mode of a service.

Inputs\:
host - Hostname or ip address.
service - Service to query.
user - Username to use for WMI impersonation on the host for this operation (can be left blank).
password - Password of the user.

Responses\:
boot - Set to boot.
system - Set to system.
automatic - Set to auto.
manual - Set to manual.
disabled - Set to disabled.
automaticDelayedStart - Set to automatic delayed start.
failure - Failed to get startup mode.
